data.description: Classic colonial home located in one of Wayne's most exclusive neighborhood with deeded rights to use Pines Lake through Indian Road access.First floor features large eat-in kitchen, formal dining room, wood paneled den with custom hardwood flooring and wood burning fire place, spacious formal living room, first floor bedroom. Second floor offers an extra large master en-suite along with three additional large bedrooms, full bathroom, extra wide hallways with hardwood floors throughout. Walk-in closets in most bedrooms. Bonus storage / potential additional room. Seasonal lake views.
